&lt;p&gt;The Marketing and Communications team leads storytelling, brand visibility, content creation, social media, campaigns, collateral, and institutional communications across ALU. In Mauritius, the team plays a key role in capturing and sharing the ALCHE student experience, campus life, academic experience, events, alumni stories, and institutional milestones.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Content Associate, Mauritius will be responsible for capturing, creating, editing, and sharing content from the Mauritius campus. This person will help tell the ALCHE story through photography, videography, social media content, student stories, event coverage, testimonials, and short-form video.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is hands-on, creative, organised, and comfortable working behind the camera as well as editing content for different platforms. They should understand social media, know how to capture strong visual stories, and be able to work closely with students, staff, faculty, and the wider marketing team.&lt;/p&gt;
