&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT ALU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ALU provides higher education for a higher purpose. Our students declare missions, not majors. They develop the real-world skills to take on the world’s most pressing challenges. And they take ownership of their learning from day one through our peer and student-led approach – because ALU believes in the power and agency of young people to start shaping the future right now.&amp;nbsp;Together with a world-class faculty and staff, our students are igniting a ripple of positive impact across Africa and the world.&lt;/p&gt;
