&lt;p&gt;You will be the person who ensures that no action item falls through the cracks. You will prepare pre-session materials for business reviews and grants portfolio reviews. You will run the post-session follow-up cycle. You will draft stakeholder communications, organize meetings across complex calendars, create clear and timely meeting minutes, and maintain the team’s operating rhythm with the precision and consistency of someone who genuinely cares about execution.&lt;/p&gt;
